        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI would actually like to check with Sebastien, if I could make a slight change to the Operational policy request.\nCan I change the input to be similar to casablanca, but the following:\n{\n\"policy-id\": \"scale.operational\",\n\"contents\" : \"<URL ESCAPED YAML>\"\n}\n\ninstead of just the Unescaped YAML. Eg make it similar to the guard policies. The problem is we should allow CLAMP to specify a name for operational and guard, rather than inferring something. There could be the possibility of clashing.",
